+# Phase 2.17 — Routing Incident RCA Route Incident Bundle Builder
+
+## Цель
+Построить единый forensic bundle именно по route-governance contour нового `routing incident RCA`.
+
+## Источники
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_results`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_verify_results`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_requests`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_results`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_rollback_journal`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_retry_requests`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_slo_rollups`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_escalations`
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_routing_apply_audit`
+
+## Выходы
+- `stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_results`
+- `metrics:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle:last`
+- `metrics:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle:<incident_id>`
+- `llm_operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundles`
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XADD stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_requests * experiment_id exp-1 ts_ms $(date +%s%3N)
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_results + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli HGETALL metrics:ml:operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle:last
+curl -s localhost:9899/metrics | grep '^ml_operator_routing_incident_rca_route_incident_bundle_'
+```
+
+## Notes
+- scope только `scanner_infra`
+- hot path не затронут
+- bundle пригоден для operator review и дальнейшего RCA bridge
